\fs30 \cf0 The review presents the algorithms used in the recommender sys- tems and focus on collaborative filtering. This review briefly describe the advantages and limitations of collaborative filtering and how this method is applied in the industry area. The review also introduces works on the methods to improve the accuracy of collaborative fil- tering and hybrid systems combining collaborative and content-based methods.
